HEADWORD: Marattiaceae
<hw>Marattiaceae</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The natural family of
ferns coextensive with the order <ord>Marattiales</ord>, consisting of
chiefly tropical eusporantiate ferns with gigantic fronds.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Marattiaceae</fam>.</syn>⟦br⟧
